WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.160
Hey, good morning everybody again. I'm going to

00:00:02.879 --> 00:00:07.199
do another video here; I'm

00:00:05.160 --> 00:00:08.580
doing them back to back. This is

00:00:07.200 --> 00:00:11.160
something the Lord brought to my

00:00:08.580 --> 00:00:13.920
attention yesterday in my prayer time. He

00:00:11.160 --> 00:00:16.379
told me that in the summer

00:00:13.920 --> 00:00:19.619
of 2022—I

00:00:16.379 --> 00:00:21.300
believe it was about this time

00:00:19.619 --> 00:00:22.680
last year, well, a little bit

00:00:21.300 --> 00:00:25.920
before because it was probably

00:00:22.680 --> 00:00:27.720
around April or so—he came to me

00:00:25.920 --> 00:00:30.359
when I was praying and said, 'Brandon,

00:00:27.720 --> 00:00:32.940
there's going to be a massive increase in the

00:00:30.359 --> 00:00:35.399
near future coming up. Oil is going to go

00:00:32.940 --> 00:00:38.040
to $200 a barrel.'He

00:00:35.399 --> 00:00:40.980
said the Prince of Saudi

00:00:38.040 --> 00:00:44.040
Arabia is going to go against the United

00:00:40.980 --> 00:00:46.260
States, and

00:00:44.040 --> 00:00:48.660
they're going to cause an oil shortage.

00:00:46.260 --> 00:00:50.519
They're going to go with

00:00:48.660 --> 00:00:53.160
Russia and

00:00:50.520 --> 00:00:54.719
China in this, and it's

00:00:53.160 --> 00:00:58.218
like a secret mission against the United

00:00:54.719 --> 00:01:01.559
States. But I saw

00:00:58.219 --> 00:01:04.739
the price of gas go to almost seven

00:01:01.559 --> 00:01:07.860
dollars a gallon again. I saw things like the

00:01:04.739 --> 00:01:08.880
price of commodities rising

00:01:07.860 --> 00:01:10.979
because they're trying to control

00:01:08.880 --> 00:01:13.020
inflation.

00:01:10.979 --> 00:01:15.479
This is all part of the

00:01:13.020 --> 00:01:18.479
global economic

00:01:15.479 --> 00:01:20.520
reset;

00:01:18.479 --> 00:01:22.619
it's part of the digital platform

00:01:20.520 --> 00:01:24.720
they're doing—creating

00:01:22.619 --> 00:01:27.180
new digital currencies and

00:01:24.720 --> 00:01:29.640
weakening the dollar.

00:01:27.180 --> 00:01:31.560
I don't know how all

00:01:29.640 --> 00:01:34.140
this happens; I'm just saying these are

00:01:31.560 --> 00:01:36.299
the parts that I see. The Lord

00:01:34.140 --> 00:01:39.000
told me that, like I said, oil would go to

00:01:36.299 --> 00:01:41.520
$200 a barrel and gas was going to go very,

00:01:39.000 --> 00:01:44.100
very high, so

00:01:41.520 --> 00:01:47.158
I just wanted to warn you about some

00:01:44.100 --> 00:01:49.619
of this stuff. Number two: this was three

00:01:47.159 --> 00:01:52.680
or four weeks ago, I believe. I was

00:01:49.619 --> 00:01:55.860
praying and the Lord showed me, 'I

00:01:52.680 --> 00:01:58.619
need you to pray for Italy.'I

00:01:55.860 --> 00:02:00.600
said, 'What's going on with

00:01:58.619 --> 00:02:02.280
Italy, Lord?'and he showed me—I

00:02:00.600 --> 00:02:04.740
had an open-eye vision again—that

00:02:02.280 --> 00:02:07.560
there's a massive

00:02:04.740 --> 00:02:10.258
volcano that's about to happen. I saw

00:02:07.560 --> 00:02:13.800
a coastline on the water,

00:02:10.258 --> 00:02:16.440
and there's a massive volcano there.

00:02:13.800 --> 00:02:19.020
He told me this is going to

00:02:16.440 --> 00:02:21.120
happen, and he said there will be signs

00:02:19.020 --> 00:02:24.420
right before there's a massive explosion.

00:02:21.120 --> 00:02:27.840
I saw it explode huge,

00:02:24.420 --> 00:02:30.540
and he kept having me pray over the

00:02:27.840 --> 00:02:34.020
ocean. There's something about

00:02:30.540 --> 00:02:35.459
the water around Italy that is

00:02:34.020 --> 00:02:38.160
very dangerous; there's

00:02:35.459 --> 00:02:39.900
like a volcano in that water, and this is

00:02:38.160 --> 00:02:43.620
going to shoot off and

00:02:39.900 --> 00:02:46.620
cause major devastation. It's

00:02:43.620 --> 00:02:48.959
going to be very serious. I've

00:02:46.620 --> 00:02:51.180
been praying for the people of Italy to

00:02:48.959 --> 00:02:53.099
wake up. If they are Christian—or if they're not—pray

00:02:51.180 --> 00:02:55.440
that they are where they're supposed

00:02:53.099 --> 00:02:58.500
to be so that they will leave when this

00:02:55.440 --> 00:03:00.260
thing goes off. There's a huge town

00:02:58.500 --> 00:03:04.140
or city

00:03:00.260 --> 00:03:07.739
on the edge of the water where I saw

00:03:04.140 --> 00:03:11.760
this volcano go off. There will be

00:03:07.739 --> 00:03:15.360
signs, maybe even on the news in Italy,

00:03:11.760 --> 00:03:18.060
about some rumblings around that area—some

00:03:15.360 --> 00:03:21.000
earthquakes

00:03:18.060 --> 00:03:24.540
or tremors—to pre-warn that something

00:03:21.000 --> 00:03:27.300
big is going to happen. Do not ignore

00:03:24.540 --> 00:03:30.900
this. It is very

00:03:27.300 --> 00:03:33.780
serious; what I saw is very serious.

00:03:30.900 --> 00:03:35.640
If you have little tremors, if you

00:03:33.780 --> 00:03:38.159
start having a lot of tremors, and you

00:03:35.640 --> 00:03:40.018
start seeing smoke or there's something

00:03:38.159 --> 00:03:40.739
going on,

00:03:40.739 --> 00:03:47.340
take heed. Be forewarned;

00:03:45.120 --> 00:03:49.560
I'm trying to tell you this is

00:03:47.340 --> 00:03:52.080
going to be a major event, an end-time

00:03:49.560 --> 00:03:55.379
event. I don't know when it's going to

00:03:52.080 --> 00:03:59.879
happen; I wish I did. I'm sorry; I only

00:03:55.379 --> 00:04:01.739
see in part and I hear in part, and so it's

00:03:59.879 --> 00:04:03.359
just stuff I'm praying over. That's

00:04:01.739 --> 00:04:06.120
basically what I had; those are two

00:04:03.360 --> 00:04:08.459
little things. I have another

00:04:06.120 --> 00:04:11.340
video I'm about to do; it'll be my third

00:04:08.459 --> 00:04:15.439
video, but this is the positive

00:04:11.340 --> 00:04:15.439
one. Have a blessed day. Bye-bye.

